{"tid":2069001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BLM系列，迦納邀請非裔美國人：我地歡迎你，回家啦","createTime":"2020-06-18T05:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T07:50:11.000Z","uid":64191,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2035d521a28945b775ae224eb647e5f3393855a8","tid":2069001,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:46:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/videos/world/2020/06/17/ghana-beyond-the-return-african-americans-george-floyd-busari-pkg-intl-ldn-vpx.cnn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Fvideos%2Fworld%2F2020%2F06%2F17%2Fghana-beyond-the-return-african-americans-george-floyd-busari-pkg-intl-ldn-vpx.cnn&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=e5732006\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Fvideos%2Fworld%2F2020%2F06%2F17%2Fghana-beyond-the-return-african-americans-george-floyd-busari-pkg-intl-ldn-vpx.cnn&h=a178e6b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/videos/world/2020/06/17/ghana-beyond-the-return-african-americans-george-floyd-busari-pkg-intl-ldn-vpx.cnn</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3201376\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3201376&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=c035d443\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3201376&h=70018ce2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3201376</a><br />\n<br />\n美國非裔男子佛洛伊德（George Floyd）遭白人警察壓頸致死事件，引發全美大規模示威抗議，非洲國家迦納現正向非裔美國人發出邀請，要他們「<span style=\"color: red;\">若覺得自己不受歡迎，非洲正在等著你們回家</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，迦納文化部長芭芭拉（Barbara Oteng-Gyasi）近日對美國非裔族群喊話，表示該國持續張開雙臂，邀請這些分隔數百年的兄弟姊妹們回家，她說，「你們不必待在不喜歡的地方，你們永遠可以選擇，非洲正等著你們回家」。<br />\n<br />\n芭芭拉進一步抨擊美國的種族主義，將其形容作「致命的流行病」，她說，這種疾病至今已有400多年歷史，而迦納希望這些遠在美國的手足們獲得治癒。<br />\n<br />\n迦納作為非洲社會較安定、經濟結構較合理的國家，去年推出「回歸之年」（The Year of the Return）政策，邀請世界各洲的非裔人士拜訪該國，迦納今年進一步打出「超越回歸」（Beyond the Return）的口號，提議非裔人士直接搬到該國定居。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n回家了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fea093a2b00df733f78880821cc14bbecdcad97","tid":2069001,"uid":133806,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2035d521a28945b775ae224eb647e5f3393855a8","tid":2069001,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:46:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/videos/world/2020/06/17/ghana-beyond-the-return-african-americans-george-floyd-busari-pkg-intl-ldn-vpx.cnn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Fvideos%2Fworld%2F2020%2F06%2F17%2Fghana-beyond-the-return-african-americans-george-floyd-busari-pkg-intl-ldn-vpx.cnn&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=e5732006\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Fvideos%2Fworld%2F2020%2F06%2F17%2Fghana-beyond-the-return-african-americans-george-floyd-busari-pkg-intl-ldn-vpx.cnn&h=a178e6b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/videos/world/2020/06/17/ghana-beyond-the-return-african-americans-george-floyd-busari-pkg-intl-ldn-vpx.cnn</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3201376\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3201376&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=c035d443\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3201376&h=70018ce2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3201376</a><br />\n<br />\n美國非裔男子佛洛伊德（George Floyd）遭白人警察壓頸致死事件，引發全美大規模示威抗議，非洲國家迦納現正向非裔美國人發出邀請，要他們「<span style=\"color: red;\">若覺得自己不受歡迎，非洲正在等著你們回家</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，迦納文化部長芭芭拉（Barbara Oteng-Gyasi）近日對美國非裔族群喊話，表示該國持續張開雙臂，邀請這些分隔數百年的兄弟姊妹們回家，她說，「你們不必待在不喜歡的